[76.39386, "o", "  \r\n    1/1 contributions submitted.\r\n    Receipt: e39268ec31ee982a...\r\n"]
[80.456421, "o", "\r\n  Three evaluations uploaded. Each hospital got a\r\n"]
[82.472843, "o", "\r\n  cryptographic receipt — proof their data was included.\r\n"]
[84.485484, "o", "\r\n  The server committed each value, added it to a Merkle\r\n"]
[86.500501, "o", "\r\n  tree, updated running sums, and discarded the individual\r\n"]
[88.509639, "o", "\r\n  values. It can never recover them.\r\n"]
[94.532334, "o", "\r\n  Next, hospitals share attack technique observations.\r\n"]
